'''馬克·威爾遜'''（{{lang-en|Marc Wilson}}；{{bd|1987年|8月17日}}）是一位[[北愛爾蘭|北愛爾蘭]]足球運動員。在場上的位置是後衛和中場。他現在效力於[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球隊[[保頓足球會|保頓]]。他雖然曾代表北愛爾蘭國青隊參賽<ref name=autogenerated1>[http://www.independent.ie/sport/soccer/wilson-aiming-to-come-of-age-73889.html Wilson aiming to come of age] {{Wayback|url=http://www.independent.ie/sport/soccer/wilson-aiming-to-come-of-age-73889.html |date=20090201014621 }} Independent.ie, 18 October 2006</ref>，但現在代表[[愛爾蘭國家足球隊|愛爾蘭]]參賽<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/euro-2016/11163222/Germany-1-Republic-of-Ireland-1-Euro-2016-qualifier-John-OShea-secures-point-after-Toni-Kroos-opener.html|title=Germany 1 Republic of Ireland 1, Euro 2016 qualifier: John O'Shea secures point after Toni Kroos' opener|date=14 October 2014|publisher=The Telegraph|access-date=2015-06-01|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411220649/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/euro-2016/11163222/Germany-1-Republic-of-Ireland-1-Euro-2016-qualifier-John-OShea-secures-point-after-Toni-Kroos-opener.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

